Algorithm:-

1.  Begin
2.  Print "Enter a number"
3.  Input n
4.  Set sum=0, c=0, j=0
5.  Repeat steps 6 to 10 from i=1 to i<n
6.  Set sum = i and j = i+1
7.  Repeat steps 8 and 9 till sum<n
8.  Set sum = sum + j
9.  Set j=j+1
10. If sum == n Goto 11 otherwise Goto 5
11. Repeat steps 12 from k=i to k<j
12. If k==i Prtint (k) otherwise Print ("+"+k)        //in same line
13. Print ""                                          //to leave a line
14. End
